metadata.name: Jack says: "11 hours and 59 minutes"
metadata.description: A 555ART production by CryptoChild 001 1/1  Crypto Twitter: it’s the good, the bad and the ugly but sometimes we get locked out, restricted, suspended or completely banned by Twitter algos or reported by a vindictive user.  ’11 hours and 59 minutes’ portrays the frustration and bewilderment when, for no known reason, we lose it all: our source of information, friends, fun and connections and might just have to get on with living in the outside world a little.   Outside where the sky is blue and you can hear the birds tweet.
